      • Alert

        public void Alert​(java.lang.String msg,
                  boolean walkover)
        Shows an alert to the GameClientHandlers connected to the game that has been won. If the alert has a result, the system of the clients is closed.
        Parameters:
        msg - message to display on the content text of the alert
        walkover - tells if the game was won with a walkover
